parameters: You see a soldier lying lifelessly on the ground.\.\.\. It appears that he tried to fight off the invaders,\. but was taken down.
Upon further inspection,\. you see a sword clutched tightly to his chest.\.\. It appears he may have not drawn it out in time to fend off his assailant.
As you try to grab the sword,\. even in death the soldier's grasp is tight.\.\. You manage to take it,\. however,\. prying it from his cold hands.
